    <item>
      <title>加拿大能源公司通过降低关税避免灾难，Gulf Outlet</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/canadian-energy-dodges-cataclysm-with-lower-tariffs-gulf-outlet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于美国总统唐纳德·特朗普下令降低原油关税，并可能让生产商完全避免对部分原油征收关税，加拿大的能源行业可能暂时躲过了与美国贸易战的灾难。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/canadian-energy-dodges-cataclysm-with-lower-tariffs-gulf-outlet</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 21:55:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>墨西哥财政部长 Sheinbaum 将于周一宣布针对关税的措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/mexico-s-sheinbaum-to-inform-measures-against-us-tariffs-monday</link>
      <description><![CDATA[墨西哥总统克劳迪娅·希因鲍姆表示，她将于周一早上宣布墨西哥政府为抵御美国关税而制定的“ B 计划”的细节。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/mexico-s-sheinbaum-to-inform-measures-against-us-tariffs-monday</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 20:49:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>新罕布什尔州丙烷价格将因早期关税影响而上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/new-hampshire-propane-prices-set-to-rise-in-early-tariff-fallout</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大进口产品征收关税可能很快就会在新英格兰地区产生影响，导致家庭取暖费用上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/new-hampshire-propane-prices-set-to-rise-in-early-tariff-fallout</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 20:23:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>卢比奥称中国在巴拿马运河的存在“不可接受”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/rubio-calls-chinese-influence-over-panama-canal-unacceptable</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国国务卿马尔科·卢比奥告诉巴拿马领导人，如果这个中美洲国家不采取行动驱逐这条关键水道附近的与中国有关联的公司，美国将保护其根据《巴拿马运河条约》享有的权利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/rubio-calls-chinese-influence-over-panama-canal-unacceptable</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 19:39:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税冲击汽车行业，汽车价格可能上涨 3,000 美元</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/car-prices-face-3-000-increase-as-trump-tariffs-hit-auto-sector</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普对加拿大和墨西哥征收的关税将威胁到北美各地汽车制造商的生产，并导致汽车价格创下新高，约 2500 亿美元的贸易将受到影响。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/car-prices-face-3-000-increase-as-trump-tariffs-hit-auto-sector</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 18:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>华盛顿 67 名飞机失事遇难者中 55 人的遗体被找到并确认身份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-02/families-visit-crash-site-days-after-the-deadliest-us-air-disaster-in-a-generation</link>
      <description><![CDATA[弗吉尼亚州阿灵顿（美联社）——当局周日称，他们已经找到 2001 年以来美国最严重的空难中遇难者 67 人中的 55 人的遗体。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/en/news/thp/2025-02-02/families-visit-crash-site-days-after-the-deadliest-us-air-disaster-in-a-generation</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 15:40:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>安大略省为应对关税，将从商店中撤下美国酒类</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/ontario-s-ford-pulls-us-alcohol-from-shelves-in-tariff-response</link>
      <description><![CDATA[加拿大两个最大的省份表示，他们将把美国产品从国营酒类商店中撤下，以回应特朗普总统对加拿大进口产品征收 25% 的关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/ontario-s-ford-pulls-us-alcohol-from-shelves-in-tariff-response</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 14:40:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税闪电战可能会使从牛油果到汽车等产品变得更加昂贵</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-s-new-tariff-blitz-to-hit-avocados-cars-and-bell-peppers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国总统唐纳德·特朗普即将对来自加拿大和墨西哥的商品征收 25% 的关税，并对来自中国的产品征收 10% 的关税，这一举措将对美国家庭产生影响，导致蔬菜、水果和汽车等多种商品的价格上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/trump-s-new-tariff-blitz-to-hit-avocados-cars-and-bell-peppers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>叙利亚总统首次出访利雅得会见 MBS</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/syria-s-interim-president-in-saudi-arabia-on-first-foreign-trip</link>
      <description><![CDATA[叙利亚临时总统艾哈迈德·沙拉在利雅得与沙特王储穆罕默德·本·萨勒曼就两国广泛的经济合作举行了会谈，叙利亚新领导人希望在其首次正式出访期间获得沙特的支持。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-02/syria-s-interim-president-in-saudi-arabia-on-first-foreign-trip</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 02 Feb 2025 10:23:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
